  SCIENCE FACTS
============================================================

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Planck's Constant
Formula: h = 6.626×10⁻³⁴ J·s
Note:    Quantum of action; E = hf for photon energy

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Speed of Light
Formula: c = 299,792,458 m/s in vacuum
Note:    Foundation of special relativity; universal speed limit

Domain:  Biology
Topic:   Cell Theory
Formula: All life is made of cells arising from pre-existing cells
Note:    Foundation of modern biology

Domain:  Chemistry
Topic:   Ideal Gas Law
Formula: PV = nRT
Note:    Pressure, volume, temperature relationship for ideal gas

Domain:  Mathematics
Topic:   Euler's Number
Formula: e ≈ 2.71828182845...
Note:    Base of natural logarithm; fundamental to calculus

